  "title": "Sales Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead Generation</li>\n  <li>Client Acquisition</li>\n  <li>Technical Presentations &amp; Demos</li>\n  <li>Proposal Development</li>\n  <li>Pipeline Management</li>\n  <li>Sales Strategy</li>\n  <li>Sales Target Achievement</li>\n  <li>Customer Relationship Management</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in Engineering or any related field.</li>\n  <li>Open for fresh graduates with interest in a sales role and willingness to learn.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience as a Sales Engineer or in a similar technical sales role is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and likeable personality.</li>\n  <li>Goal driven and result-oriented</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in MS office and basic knowledge on Autocad is required.</li>\n  <li>Strong problem-solving abilities and attention to detail.</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in technical writing and documentation.</li>\n  <li>Strong organizational and project management skills.</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of technical concepts and ability to explain them to a non-technical audience.</li>\n  <li>Ability in negotiating terms and closing a deal.</li>\n</ul>",
